      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely (including the stalks)</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
