    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[250ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
