      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chilli con carne</strong> over the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>baked sweet potato</strong> and dollop the <strong>smashed avocado</strong> on top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, a <strong>lime wedge</strong> and a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
